<p>ActiveControl is a change management tool that is designed to streamline the SAP change process. It provides a comprehensive set of features for managing and controlling changes, including transport management, workflow, testing, and approvals. ActiveControl is a third-party tool that is designed to work alongside SAP systems, and itâ€™s compatible with both ECC and S/4HANA.</p>

